    javax.servlet.Filter

    public class Cas20ServiceTicketJsonValidationFilter
extends org.jasig.cas.client.validation.AbstractTicketValidationFilter
    An implementation of the AbstractTicketValidationFilter that designates the ticket validator object to be an instance of Cas20ServiceTicketJsonValidator

    The configuration of this filter is similar to Cas20ProxyReceivingTicketValidationFilter
    Since:
    0.6
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed, Unicon, inc.
